com.gl.vn.me.ko.sample.instrumentation.example.proxy

Class MapProxyFactoryExampleC

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gl.vn.me.ko.sample.instrumentation.example.proxy.MapProxyFactoryExampleC

  • public final class MapProxyFactoryExampleC
extends Object
    The class provides an ability to create a Java-proxy object of type Map that can intercept invocation of any method of interface Map and perform additional actions (see InvocationHandlerExampleC.invoke(Object, Method, Object[])).

    Instantiability: forbidden.
    Thread safety: thread-safe.

    See Also:
